But now there's also Wan Xinxin.

279
00:17:40,160 --> 00:17:41,360
Because Xinxin says between us,

280
00:17:41,360 --> 00:17:43,160
we lack basic trust and understanding.

281
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:44,320
I think she's right.

282
00:17:45,760 --> 00:17:48,020
Things will work out when the time comes.

283
00:17:48,040 --> 00:17:48,360
Zhongxin.

284
00:17:48,360 --> 00:17:49,360
I actually think

285
00:17:49,360 --> 00:17:49,800
Zhongxin.

286
00:17:49,800 --> 00:17:50,480
you might as well

287
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:52,740
take this opportunity to visit America.

288
00:17:52,880 --> 00:17:53,280
Zhongxin.

289
00:17:53,280 --> 00:17:55,840
Spend some time living with Xiaqing and Ruirui.

290
00:17:55,840 --> 00:17:58,600
During this time, perhaps you

291
00:17:59,320 --> 00:18:01,600
will gain a new perspective

292
00:18:01,840 --> 00:18:03,970
on your relationship with Wan Xinxin.

293
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:05,000
Don't you think?

294
00:18:09,080 --> 00:18:10,840
Okay, thank you.

295
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:13,400
Please take another look at this proposal.

296
00:18:18,720 --> 00:18:19,720
Hello.

297
00:18:22,040 --> 00:18:22,800
Sir,

298
00:18:22,800 --> 00:18:25,520
your attire doesn't meet our club's dress code.

299
00:18:26,320 --> 00:18:27,980
What's wrong with my clothes?

300
00:18:28,120 --> 00:18:30,320
This is the trendiest outfit this year.

301
00:18:30,360 --> 00:18:31,720
Excuse me, he's with me.

302
00:18:31,720 --> 00:18:32,720
Please let him in.

303
00:18:33,360 --> 00:18:34,880
Alright, please come in.

304
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:39,280
Miss Xia, your drink.

305
00:18:39,560 --> 00:18:40,240
Thank you.

306
00:18:42,040 --> 00:18:43,160
It's getting late.

307
00:18:43,640 --> 00:18:45,680
If you're hungry, let's order some food.

308
00:18:45,680 --> 00:18:47,400
Okay, don't mind if I do.

309
00:18:59,640 --> 00:19:01,170
Hello, what would you like?

310
00:19:01,800 --> 00:19:03,530
Hello sir, what would you like?

311
00:19:04,440 --> 00:19:05,840
I'll have the same as her.

312
00:19:07,200 --> 00:19:07,800
Thank you.

313
00:19:10,680 --> 00:19:12,680
What did you want to talk to me about?

314
00:19:16,280 --> 00:19:16,760
Ms. Xia.

315
00:19:17,680 --> 00:19:19,960
You look so elegant and classy,

316
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:23,880
yet you keep doing such tasteless things.

317
00:19:25,440 --> 00:19:27,720
I don't understand what you're talking about.

318
00:19:27,720 --> 00:19:28,980
Do I have to expose you?

319
00:19:30,240 --> 00:19:30,600
Fine.

320
00:19:32,360 --> 00:19:34,160
You told Wan Xinxin

321
00:19:34,520 --> 00:19:36,180
that Huaming proposed to you.

322
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:38,640
Do you have any questions?

323
00:19:38,640 --> 00:19:39,880
I have major doubts.

324
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:42,660
That video alone raises many questions.

325
00:19:44,440 --> 00:19:45,370
What questions?

326
00:19:45,480 --> 00:19:47,940
What did Huaming say when he proposed to you?

327
00:19:49,960 --> 00:19:51,690
Hello sir. Your special drink.

328
00:19:51,840 --> 00:19:52,440
Thank you.

329
00:19:53,560 --> 00:19:56,760
How could you not know what's said in a proposal?

330
00:19:58,320 --> 00:20:00,120
Fine. Let's not talk about that.

331
00:20:00,160 --> 00:20:02,920
Then let me ask you, where's your engagement ring?

332
00:20:02,920 --> 00:20:03,520
If Huaming

333
00:20:04,480 --> 00:20:06,120
really proposed to you,

334
00:20:06,480 --> 00:20:07,440
then the ring he gave you

335
00:20:07,440 --> 00:20:08,840
would be identical to Wan Xinxin's.

336
00:20:08,840 --> 00:20:10,300
Why aren't you wearing it?

337
00:20:13,320 --> 00:20:14,250
I left it at home.

338
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:16,840
I don't want to wear the same thing as Wan Xinxin.

339
00:20:16,840 --> 00:20:17,970
Is that not allowed?

340
00:20:18,360 --> 00:20:19,360
This single woman

341
00:20:19,400 --> 00:20:21,360
fantasizing like this in broad daylight,

342
00:20:21,360 --> 00:20:22,420
quite impressive.

343
00:20:26,880 --> 00:20:27,640
Mr. Xu,

344
00:20:28,360 --> 00:20:29,840
what exactly are you trying to say?

345
00:20:29,840 --> 00:20:31,570
Huaming never proposed to you.

346
00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:34,360
That video was just an act between you two.

347
00:20:34,360 --> 00:20:35,560
You think I don't know

348
00:20:36,680 --> 00:20:37,360
these kinds of tricks?

349
00:20:37,360 --> 00:20:40,620
You may fool Wan Xinxin, but you can't fool me, understand?

350
00:20:42,680 --> 00:20:44,040
Mom, you're here.

351
00:20:45,240 --> 00:20:47,170
School's over, Ruirui. Come here.

352
00:20:51,120 --> 00:20:52,920
Who is he? A garbage collector?

353
00:20:55,400 --> 00:20:56,120
He is

354
00:20:56,400 --> 00:20:59,200
Wan Xinxin's best friend. His name is Xu Ke.

355
00:21:00,200 --> 00:21:03,240
I heard there's no such thing as platonic friendship between men and women.

356
00:21:03,240 --> 00:21:05,370
You like Sister Xinxin too, don't you?

357
00:21:05,840 --> 00:21:06,440
Oh my!

358
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:08,760
Kids these days are so straightforward.

359
00:21:08,760 --> 00:21:10,240
Look, I need to talk to your mom.

360
00:21:10,240 --> 00:21:11,040
Don't interrupt us.

361
00:21:11,040 --> 00:21:12,900
Just stand aside and watch, okay?

362
00:21:13,040 --> 00:21:14,400
Who says this doesn't concern me?

363
00:21:14,400 --> 00:21:16,130
Mom's business is my business.

364
00:21:18,760 --> 00:21:20,160
I just came from Huaming.

365
00:21:20,800 --> 00:21:21,560
He told me

366
00:21:21,720 --> 00:21:23,120
he never proposed to you.

367
00:21:23,200 --> 00:21:24,000
So what?

368
00:21:24,880 --> 00:21:25,800
He's already agreed

369
00:21:25,800 --> 00:21:27,960
to go back to America with us and remarry me.

370
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:29,320
That's right. Dad belongs to us.

371
00:21:29,320 --> 00:21:31,360
Don't even think about taking him away.

372
00:21:31,360 --> 00:21:33,000
Fine. You two can say whatever you want.

373
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:33,920
Anyway, now

374
00:21:33,920 --> 00:21:35,520
you're admitting this video is fake,

375
00:21:35,520 --> 00:21:36,040
right?

376
00:21:36,240 --> 00:21:38,720
Then I'll clarify this with Wan Xinxin.

377
00:21:39,040 --> 00:21:41,080
When the time comes, who gets Huaming

378
00:21:41,080 --> 00:21:41,760
is still uncertain.

379
00:21:41,760 --> 00:21:43,620
Why don't you two compete fairly?

380
00:21:44,360 --> 00:21:45,820
Then we'll see how it goes.

381
00:21:45,880 --> 00:21:47,140
Ruirui, let's go home.

382
00:21:52,920 --> 00:21:55,760
Mr. Xu, it tastes better with this added.

383
00:21:56,680 --> 00:21:57,880
Thank you, kid.

384
00:21:58,880 --> 00:22:00,080
Ruirui, let's go.

385
00:22:02,840 --> 00:22:03,680
Goodbye.

386
00:22:12,080 --> 00:22:12,880
Wait a minute.

387
00:22:13,480 --> 00:22:15,000
Hold on, you two haven't paid yet.

388
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:16,080
Call them back.

389
00:22:16,560 --> 00:22:18,840
Sir, the food plus service charge and private room fee

390
00:22:18,840 --> 00:22:20,680
comes to a total of 998 yuan.

391
00:22:22,560 --> 00:22:23,040
How much?

392
00:22:23,040 --> 00:22:24,000
998.

393
00:22:24,800 --> 00:22:26,720
998?

394
00:22:28,440 --> 00:22:29,970
For these two lousy dishes?

395
00:22:31,800 --> 00:22:32,480
Oh my god!

396
00:22:46,680 --> 00:22:48,740
Our proposal video has been exposed.

397
00:22:50,280 --> 00:22:52,040
Looks like we need to find a way

398
00:22:52,040 --> 00:22:53,960
to get your father to leave here as soon as possible

399
00:22:53,960 --> 00:22:55,760
and come back to America with us.

400
00:22:55,800 --> 00:22:57,200
Mom, what should we do?

401
00:22:57,200 --> 00:22:58,730
Please think of something.

402
00:22:59,800 --> 00:23:02,440
I do have an idea.

403
00:23:03,240 --> 00:23:03,880
What is it?

404
00:23:34,960 --> 00:23:36,240
Let's dance.

405
00:24:51,600 --> 00:24:52,440
Dad.

406
00:24:53,080 --> 00:24:56,340
I've been happy these days since I came back. How about you?

407
00:24:58,880 --> 00:25:00,040
I'm very happy too.

408
00:25:00,440 --> 00:25:01,040
Dad,

409
00:25:04,400 --> 00:25:06,600
why are you listening to such a sad song?

410
00:25:07,680 --> 00:25:09,880
Do you understand what this song means?

411
00:25:16,280 --> 00:25:18,760
Dad, I know.

412
00:25:21,200 --> 00:25:23,120
Mom and I coming back

413
00:25:23,520 --> 00:25:25,650
caused you and Sister Xinxin to fight.

414
00:25:26,360 --> 00:25:28,720
But Mom and I both hope

415
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:30,560
that you can live happily.

416
00:25:33,440 --> 00:25:34,400
I know.

417
00:25:35,000 --> 00:25:37,160
I also want Ruirui to be happy.

418
00:25:40,720 --> 00:25:42,600
Dad, you know what?

419
00:25:42,920 --> 00:25:44,320
My classmates always ask

420
00:25:44,320 --> 00:25:46,800
why my dad doesn't live with my mom.

421
00:25:47,960 --> 00:25:49,440
I tell them my dad

422
00:25:49,600 --> 00:25:51,960
is the bravest and coolest dad,

423
00:25:54,360 --> 00:25:55,480
like Batman.

424
00:25:58,280 --> 00:26:00,480
Really, China needs him,

425
00:26:00,480 --> 00:26:02,040
he can't just leave.

426
00:26:03,760 --> 00:26:06,760
All the other kids have lots of photos with their dads.

427
00:26:07,920 --> 00:26:10,600
But I want to take many photos with you too.

428
00:26:12,080 --> 00:26:14,360
I know you love me the most.

429
00:26:26,640 --> 00:26:28,280
Dad, I know

430
00:26:28,520 --> 00:26:30,800
you've always liked Sister Xinxin.

431
00:26:31,200 --> 00:26:33,720
If I ask you to come with us to America,

432
00:26:34,640 --> 00:26:36,100
you won't be happy either.

433
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:39,600
But I know,

434
00:26:40,440 --> 00:26:42,920
Dad, you will always love me.

435
00:26:43,880 --> 00:26:47,720
It's okay. When I grow up and make money,

436
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:48,640
I hope we

437
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:50,840
can come back to see you every week

438
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:53,800
and take lots of photos with you.

439
00:26:53,880 --> 00:26:55,610
I'll send them to my classmates

440
00:26:56,120 --> 00:26:57,400
so they can see

441
00:26:58,120 --> 00:27:00,120
how much my dad likes me

442
00:27:00,120 --> 00:27:01,200
and loves me.

443
00:27:24,680 --> 00:27:26,440
Dad, do you know

444
00:27:26,680 --> 00:27:27,840
my classmates ask me

445
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:30,520
why my dad isn't with my mom?

446
00:27:34,640 --> 00:27:37,880
All the other kids have lots of photos with their dads.

447
00:27:39,080 --> 00:27:41,680
But I want to take many photos with you too.

448
00:27:43,040 --> 00:27:45,120
I know you love me the most.

449
00:28:16,560 --> 00:28:19,120
What's this? Are you really leaving?

450
00:28:20,560 --> 00:28:21,120
Yes.

451
00:28:22,680 --> 00:28:24,210
Yes? What do you mean 'yes'?

452
00:28:27,800 --> 00:28:31,060
The battle hasn't even begun and you're already giving up.

453
00:28:31,520 --> 00:28:33,180
Have some backbone, will you?

454
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:35,400
Where's that fierce attitude

455
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:37,400
you had when you lectured me before?

456
00:28:37,960 --> 00:28:39,360
Think about it.

457
00:28:39,520 --> 00:28:41,580
One is older than you, one is younger.

458
00:28:42,400 --> 00:28:43,660
What are you afraid of?

459
00:28:44,600 --> 00:28:47,200
What are you running from? What are you scared of?

460
00:28:47,200 --> 00:28:48,080
I'm not afraid.

461
00:28:48,360 --> 00:28:50,240
I've really decided to go to France.

462
00:28:50,240 --> 00:28:51,370
Don't try to stop me.

463
00:28:52,560 --> 00:28:53,760
They're not scary.

464
00:28:54,320 --> 00:28:55,000
But whenever they

465
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:56,560
appear in my life

466
00:28:56,720 --> 00:28:58,560
everything becomes a mess

467
00:28:58,760 --> 00:28:59,960
that I can't sort out.

468
00:29:00,720 --> 00:29:01,480
I give up.

469
00:29:04,120 --> 00:29:07,040
No way. I don't agree. Stop packing.

470
00:29:07,160 --> 00:29:09,360
I even met with that Xia Qing for your sake.

471
00:29:09,360 --> 00:29:10,720
Don't you want to know what happened?

472
00:29:10,720 --> 00:29:12,720
The results don't matter anymore.

473
00:29:14,720 --> 00:29:15,800
Alright, stop packing.

474
00:29:15,800 --> 00:29:17,040
Stop packing, will you?

475
00:29:17,040 --> 00:29:18,680
What are you doing, Xu Ke?

476
00:29:19,200 --> 00:29:21,130
What do you mean? Look at yourself.

477
00:29:21,280 --> 00:29:22,320
You're a mess.

478
00:29:22,480 --> 00:29:24,240
Are you still the Wan Xinxin I know?

479
00:29:24,240 --> 00:29:25,920
Just because of those two people

480
00:29:25,920 --> 00:29:28,480
you're willingly giving up your own happiness.

481
00:29:28,480 --> 00:29:30,810
Aren't you afraid you'll regret it later?

482
00:29:31,080 --> 00:29:31,840
Happiness?

483
00:29:32,800 --> 00:29:34,360
I feel like I'm the most

484
00:29:34,360 --> 00:29:36,760
unfortunate person in the world right now.

485
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:41,960
Fine. Let me ask you one last question.

486
00:29:42,480 --> 00:29:43,940
Do you still love Hua Ming?

487
00:29:53,400 --> 00:29:55,400
The answer doesn't matter anymore.

488
00:29:55,920 --> 00:29:59,120
He's getting back together with his ex-wife.

489
00:29:59,840 --> 00:30:00,720
Then let me tell you.

490
00:30:00,720 --> 00:30:01,640
What if I told you

491
00:30:01,640 --> 00:30:02,960
that video was fake?

492
00:30:04,560 --> 00:30:07,200
What if I've already proven

493
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:09,080
that Hua Ming was practicing proposing with his ex-wife

494
00:30:09,080 --> 00:30:10,560
so he could propose to you?

495
00:30:12,520 --> 00:30:14,080
I don't understand what nonsense you're talking about.

496
00:30:14,080 --> 00:30:14,920
And I don't want to hear it.

497
00:30:14,920 --> 00:30:17,180
Hua Ming and I can't go back to how we were.

498
00:30:17,960 --> 00:30:19,280
Fine.

499
00:30:19,280 --> 00:30:20,480
I'll say no more.

500
00:30:20,800 --> 00:30:22,480
Anyway, I've already found the mother and daughter.

501
00:30:22,480 --> 00:30:24,680
They'll surely have a plan in the future.

502
00:30:24,680 --> 00:30:26,280
Whether Hua Ming stays or not

503
00:30:26,960 --> 00:30:28,490
depends on what you do next.

504
00:30:28,800 --> 00:30:29,530
I'm leaving.

505
00:30:29,600 --> 00:30:31,560
Why are you causing trouble for me?

506
00:30:31,560 --> 00:30:33,560
Think about it carefully yourself.

507
00:30:41,200 --> 00:30:42,760
Ruirui, dinner's almost ready.

508
00:30:42,760 --> 00:30:44,440
Dad, come quickly!

509
00:30:44,960 --> 00:30:47,360
Mom's heart condition is acting up and she has a fever too.

510
00:30:47,360 --> 00:30:49,480
Hurry up!

511
00:30:54,160 --> 00:30:56,290
What's wrong? Are you feeling unwell?

512
00:30:59,400 --> 00:31:00,660
It's nothing serious.

513
00:31:01,080 --> 00:31:02,120
Just a headache.

514
00:31:05,440 --> 00:31:06,520
Um, look, Ruirui.

515
00:31:06,520 --> 00:31:08,200
Mom says she's fine. She'll feel better soon.

516
00:31:08,200 --> 00:31:10,200
Why don't you take her temperature?

517
00:31:10,320 --> 00:31:12,600
Mom doesn't have a fever.

518
00:31:13,320 --> 00:31:14,520
Check it properly!

519
00:31:17,160 --> 00:31:18,820
Mom's temperature is normal.

520
00:31:18,960 --> 00:31:21,000
Dad, you're a doctor.

521
00:31:21,040 --> 00:31:22,040
You should know

522
00:31:22,040 --> 00:31:24,840
what the most accurate way to take temperature is.

523
00:31:25,640 --> 00:31:27,920
Isn't it using your lips to check?

524
00:31:28,280 --> 00:31:29,520
When I had a fever as a child,

525
00:31:29,520 --> 00:31:31,520
that's how you always checked mine.

526
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:39,280
Hmm, Mom does have a slight fever.

527
00:31:39,680 --> 00:31:42,200


528
00:31:43,640 --> 00:31:44,160
Dad.

529
00:31:44,800 --> 00:31:47,520
Do you know where the most comfortable place is?

530
00:31:47,520 --> 00:31:48,520
What place?

531
00:31:48,640 --> 00:31:49,680
Dad's shoulder.

532
00:31:49,880 --> 00:31:52,880
Mom, lean on Dad's shoulder now.

533
00:31:52,960 --> 00:31:55,200
Hurry up. It'll be over soon.

534
00:32:00,960 --> 00:32:03,520
Dad, you know what?

535
00:32:04,200 --> 00:32:06,400
Mom and I often get sick in America.

536
00:32:06,800 --> 00:32:09,530
Let's all three of us go back to America together.

537
00:32:09,720 --> 00:32:13,400
The two of us can take care of Mom. Wouldn't that be nice?

538
00:32:14,720 --> 00:32:17,040
Ruirui...

539
00:32:17,280 --> 00:32:18,800
Dad, you don't need to say anything.

540
00:32:18,800 --> 00:32:20,800
I'll give you time to think about it.

541
00:32:29,720 --> 00:32:30,240
Ruirui.

542
00:32:32,560 --> 00:32:34,920
Dad promises you

543
00:32:35,240 --> 00:32:37,480
to go back to America with you for school.

544
00:32:37,480 --> 00:32:38,680
Really, Dad?

545
00:32:38,880 --> 00:32:41,320
Great! I'll book the tickets right now.

546
00:32:47,400 --> 00:32:49,200
My daughter has really grown up.

547
00:32:51,400 --> 00:32:53,730
Thank you for playing along with us today.

548
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:57,440
Ruirui really hopes you can go with her.

549
00:32:57,720 --> 00:32:59,640
I understand.

550
00:33:01,160 --> 00:33:04,160
When did you decide to come with us to America?

551
00:33:05,360 --> 00:33:06,960
Dr. Chen talked to me.

552
00:33:07,240 --> 00:33:09,800
He said I should go to America with you.

553
00:33:10,720 --> 00:33:11,200
Also,

554
00:33:12,520 --> 00:33:14,600
Ruirui asked me for a dance that day,

555
00:33:15,040 --> 00:33:16,500
and she told me something.

556
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:19,330
I've made up my mind.

557
00:33:19,800 --> 00:33:22,000
I should go to America with my daughter.

558
