593
00:35:20,480 --> 00:35:23,160
It needs time and experience to polish it.

594
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:30,480
I really wish we could go back to the past.

595
00:35:31,560 --> 00:35:33,120
Living that carefree life.

596
00:35:34,360 --> 00:35:34,890
Xiaqing.

597
00:35:37,160 --> 00:35:38,820
All the memories from the past

598
00:35:39,880 --> 00:35:41,720
will stay right here.

599
00:35:42,320 --> 00:35:43,760
Right here.

600
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:46,040
But the past is the past.

601
00:35:48,400 --> 00:35:49,600
We can't go back.

602
00:35:52,160 --> 00:35:53,160
You know what?

603
00:35:54,000 --> 00:35:56,530
Ruirui has grown up and I feel I've gotten old.

604
00:35:56,920 --> 00:35:58,650
I've become a middle-aged man.

605
00:35:59,880 --> 00:36:01,000
During these three years since you left,

606
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:03,000
I've been living in this apartment.

607
00:36:03,320 --> 00:36:04,880
Sometimes I just sit in this spot,

608
00:36:04,880 --> 00:36:08,210
right here where I am now, looking out the window, thinking.

609
00:36:10,360 --> 00:36:12,420
My life had already lost its passion,

610
00:36:13,160 --> 00:36:15,120
