611
00:36:15,120 --> 00:36:17,320
and no one able to enter my heart.

612
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:18,900
Except for Ruirui.

613
00:36:20,400 --> 00:36:22,460
But then Wan Xinxin and Bao appeared.

614
00:36:22,960 --> 00:36:24,840
She really entered my heart.

615
00:36:26,760 --> 00:36:29,360
That passion and youthful feeling I hadn't felt for so long

616
00:36:29,360 --> 00:36:31,160
came back. Really.

617
00:36:33,560 --> 00:36:35,160
I really like Wan Xinxin.

618
00:36:38,880 --> 00:36:40,210
Huaming, I understand.

619
00:36:41,760 --> 00:36:46,080
I know. Three years ago when I took Ruirui back to America,

620
00:36:46,880 --> 00:36:48,160
I caused you significant pain.

621
00:36:48,160 --> 00:36:49,760
It was because I was selfish.

622
00:36:49,880 --> 00:36:50,920
But you know,

623
00:36:51,120 --> 00:36:52,720
I just wanted to give Ruirui a

624
00:36:52,720 --> 00:36:54,400
better living environment.

625
00:36:55,240 --> 00:36:56,040
I just hoped

626
00:36:56,120 --> 00:36:58,760
my career would develop better.

627
00:36:59,760 --> 00:37:00,960
Can you understand what I mean?

628
00:37:00,960 --> 00:37:02,480
I can understand what you mean.

629
00:37:02,480 --> 00:37:04,760
But Xiaqing, I want you to know that

630
00:37:06,200 --> 00:37:08,920
you, me, and Ruirui will always be a family.

631
00:37:09,720 --> 00:37:10,180
Really.

632
00:37:10,560 --> 00:37:11,920
Ruirui is our joint creation.

633
00:37:11,920 --> 00:37:13,080
We're proud of her.

634
00:37:15,280 --> 00:37:17,210
But we can never go back to the past.

635
00:37:28,000 --> 00:37:29,080
He hasn't

636
00:37:29,160 --> 00:37:30,690
