640
00:37:37,480 --> 00:37:38,800
Look at the ring you're wearing.

641
00:37:38,800 --> 00:37:40,280
It's still the one he gave you

642
00:37:40,280 --> 00:37:41,360
when he proposed.

643
00:37:43,880 --> 00:37:46,480
It's such a big diamond, I might as well wear it.

644
00:37:46,560 --> 00:37:49,000
If things don't work out for me in France someday,

