657
00:38:19,120 --> 00:38:20,760
Mommy will be back in a year.

658
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:21,960
Sad.

659
00:38:22,240 --> 00:38:24,240
After a year, I'll come back for you.

660
00:38:27,280 --> 00:38:28,440
You'll miss mommy.

661
00:38:29,120 --> 00:38:29,640
Come.

662
00:38:30,280 --> 00:38:31,640
Well, since you've made up your mind,

663
00:38:31,640 --> 00:38:32,970
