677
00:39:11,480 --> 00:39:12,760
Didn't someone just say

678
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:14,960
they needed to learn to be independent?

679
00:39:15,400 --> 00:39:17,960
Face your own issues yourself, right?

680
00:39:34,360 --> 00:39:36,640
Playing the grand piano in America.

