00:41:00,960 --> 00:41:01,680
Um,

687
00:41:02,520 --> 00:41:04,720
that bell that baby boy always likes.

688
00:41:06,840 --> 00:41:09,170
I wanted to get it because I'm afraid he'll

689
00:41:09,960 --> 00:41:11,290
keep crying without it.

